#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.static_print"
msgstr "# triton.language.static_print"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:2
msgid "## 1.函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:4
msgid "`static_print` 用于在编译时打印信息，类似于Python的`print()`函数，但它在内核编译期间执行而不是运行时执行。"
msgstr "`static_print` is used to print information at compile time, similar to Python's `print()` function, but it executes during kernel compilation rather than at runtime."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.static_print(*values, sep: str = ' ', end: str = '\\n', file=None, flush=False, _semantic=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:8
msgid "## 2.规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数 | 类型 | 默认值 | 含义说明 |\n"
"|------|------|--------|----------|\n"
"| `values`| `tensor`/`scalar`| 必需 | 要打印的值，支持多个参数 |\n"
"| `sep` | `str` | `' '` | 值之间的分隔符 |\n"
"| `end` | `str` | `'\\n'` | 打印结束时的后缀 |\n"
"|`file` | - | - | 写入的文件对象 |\n"
"|`flush` | `bool` | `False` | 是否刷新输出缓冲区 |\n"
"|`_semantic` | - | - | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Default | Description |\n"
"|-----------|------|---------|-------------|\n"
"| `values` | `tensor`/`scalar` | Required | Values to print, supports multiple arguments |\n"
"| `sep` | `str` | `' '` | Separator between values |\n"
"| `end` | `str` | `'\\n'` | Suffix at the end of printing |\n"
"| `file` | - | - | File object to write to |\n"
"| `flush` | `bool` | `False` | Whether to flush the output buffer |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | - | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported for now |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:14
msgid "### 2.2.1 Data Type 支持"
msgstr "### 2.2.1 Data Type Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:16
msgid "A3："
msgstr "A3:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:18
msgid ""
"| | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"|------|-------|-------|-------|-------|--------|--------|--------|-------|------|------|------|------|------|\n"
"| GPU | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | ×| × | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
msgstr ""
"| | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"|------|-------|-------|-------|-------|--------|--------|--------|-------|------|------|------|------|------|\n"
"| GPU | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | ×| × | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | ✓ | ✓ |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:20
msgid "### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:22
msgid ""
"|        | 支持维度范围          |\n"
"| ------ | --------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
"| Ascend | 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | Supported Dimension Range |\n"
"| ------ | ----------------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | Only supports 1~5D tensor |\n"
"| Ascend | Only supports 1~5D tensor |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:24
msgid "结论：在 Shape 方面，GPU 与 Ascend 平台无差异，均支持 1 至 5 维张量。"
msgstr "Conclusion: In terms of Shape, there is no difference between GPU and Ascend platforms; both support 1 to 5-dimensional tensors."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:26
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Restrictions"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:28
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "Relative community capability is lacking and cannot be achieved."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:30
msgid "Ascend 对比 GPU 缺失uint8、uint16、uint32、uint64、fp64的支持能力（硬件限制）。"
msgstr "Ascend lacks support for uint8, uint16, uint32, uint64, and fp64 compared to GPU (hardware limitation)."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:32
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:34
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"import triton.language as tl\n"
"\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def basic_static_print_example(x_ptr, BLOCK_SIZE: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    # 在编译时打印常量的值\n"
"    tl.static_print(\"BLOCK_SIZE =\", BLOCK_SIZE)\n"
"    tl.static_print(BLOCK_SIZE)\n"
"    # 支持fstring打印方式\n"
"    tl.static_print(f\"BLOCK_SIZE={BLOCK_SIZE}\")\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:36
msgid "如果打印的**非常量**结果，会打印一个`数据类型[数据shape(标量为空)]`的值，如果下面的代码`x_ptr`指向的数据类型为`int32`就会打印`val:int32[constexpr[4]]`的结果"
msgstr "If printing a **non-constant** result, it will print a value in the format `data type[data shape (scalar is empty)]`. For example, if the data type pointed to by `x_ptr` in the code below is `int32`, it will print the result `val:int32[constexpr[4]]`."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Debug_Ops/static_print.md:38
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"import triton.language as tl\n"
"\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def basic_static_print_example(x_ptr, BLOCK_SIZE: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    idx = tl.arange(0, 4)\n"
"    val = tl.load(x_ptr + idx)\n"
"    tl.static_print(\"val:\",val)\n"
"    #非常量不支持fstring打印\n"
"    #tl.static_print(f\"val:{val}\")\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

